A2984 &Cx1f; tad-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ONLINE-SHABBAT30-COX     06-29 0545
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ONLINE-SHABBAT30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CD-ROM aims to bring Jews back to the fold
 &HT;    By Douglas Belkin
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
