<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FEATURES-BJT30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE FEATURES BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These feature stories are moving today to clients of the New
York Times News Service. Stories are for release Wednesday, June
30, 1999, unless otherwise embargoed.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET BUDGET INFORMATION
</P>
<P>
