<P>
   FOOD-TASTE _ Jill Wendholt Silva, food editor for the Kansas
City Star, writes a weekly column about cooking and nutrition. This
week: Seeking spirituality through food. Story will move in the
``l'' category.
</P>
<P>
   FOOD-TORTE _ What do an ice cream torte and a skyscraper have in
common?
</P>
<P>
   Blueprints. Engineers wouldn't dream of constructing a column of
granite, steel and glass without a plan to ensure its stability.
Kudos to the smart cookie who invented springform pans to hold
dense desserts built on fragile crumb crusts. So here's a blueprint
for building your own frozen ice cream torte. By JILL WENDHOLT
SILVA. Story will move in the ``l'' category.
