</P>
<P>
   THIRD _ Dennis Moore is a freshman Democrat in a Kansas
congressional district that was Republican for generations, but
even this far out, more area Republicans are taking themselves out
of the race than jumping into it. Things that worry them: the usual
split between GOP factions in Johnson County and Moore's feversih
amassing of a campaign chest. Steve Kraske. 28.
