   HOUSE: A couple near Buffalo, Mo., is desperate. Their son died
in an Arkansas fire, but police never solved it. They want to start
their own investigation but have no money to do so. Their solution?
Auction off their dream home _ for a $100 entry fee, you can write
an essay about why you should win it. A story on the lengths to
which people will go. Oscar Avila. 25. Photo.
