was killed in a one-car crash. On Saturday night, her grandmother,
Margaret Belobrajdic, was killed and her grandfather, Joe
Belobarjdic, critically injured in a wreck about a mile and a half
from where Hillary died. We try again to talk with the family. Mark
Wiebe. 18.
