<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-29 13:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3198 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u t &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TRAVEL-KENYA-BOS &LR;      06-29 1340
