<P>
   The following graphics accompany the Hearst News Service story
on genetic engineering for release July 3, 1999. They are Freehand
7 documents.
</P>
<P>
   MILLENNIUM_Genetics opinions.clr -- 25p x 2 1/2 --
(BC-MILLENNIUM-GENETICS-HNS)
</P>
<P>
   Americans' opinions on genetic engineering.
</P>
