<HEADLINE>
COSMOGIRL! VS. COSMOPOLITAN: A QUICK COMPARISON
</HEADLINE>
 
(Accompanies BC-TEEN-MAGS, BC-TEEN-MAGS-RACK) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   _
</P>
<P>
   Cover
</P>
<P>
   CosmoGIRL!: Melissa Joan Hart in modest tank top and cargo pants
</P>
<P>
   Cosmopolitan: Rebecca Romijn-Stamos in two tiny swathes of cloth
</P>
<P>
   _
</P>
<P>
   Marketing ploy of the month
</P>
<P>
