<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-29 17:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3540 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN-BO     06-29 0949
