<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-SOCCER-0630-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FREE KICKS: ETHNIC ALBANIANS RETURN TO SOCCER STADIUM
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (s) Sports categories.
