   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   YUGOSLAVIA (Pristina, Yugoslavia) _ Opposition mounts first
public rally against President Slobodan Milosevic since the end of
the NATO air campaign. Wrapup. By John Donnelly. 1200 words.
</P>
