   IRELAND-TALKS (Belfast) _ Release of a report offering the last
real chance to forge a compromise over IRA weapons and clear the
way for a power-sharing government in Northern Ireland is delayed
until Wednesday. By Kevin Cullen and John O'Farrell. 850 words
</P>
