December, an array of possibilities develops for the 2000 primary
calendar. By Jill Zuckman. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   AIDS-COCKTAILS (Portland, Maine) _ As AIDS ``cocktails'' keep
patients living longer, insurers ask why they cannot go back to
work. Patients and doctors say side effects make normal work life
virtually impossible. By James Bandler. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   MA-TREASURY-SCANDAL (Boston) _ Affidavit discloses that two
arrested state Treasury employees were working together from the
start in an alleged scheme to steal $2.4 million. By Stephen
Kurkjian. 1000 words.
