<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Saturday, June 26,
about the United Nations' efforts to set up a civil administration
in Kosovo referred incorrectly to Sergio Vieira de Mello, the
Brazilian diplomat who is Secretary General Kofi Annan's special
representative to Kosovo. He did not run the United Nations mission
in Cambodia; Yasushi Akashi of Japan did.
