<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-29 20:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3785 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OBITUARY-HOOKER-BOS &LR;      06-29 1092
