<DOCNO> NYT19990629.0323 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-29 20:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3787 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HORMEL-HNS &LR;      06-29 0922
