 Tuesday, June 29, 1999    
 Editors      The Hearst News Service has filed or will file the
following for Wednesday. If you have questions, please call Susie
McBee or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about Houston
Chronicle sports stories, please call 713-220-7896.    (Adds:
