   Name: May be hoping Radojevic slides or that Northwestern's Evan
Eschmeyer (6-11) becomes athletic overnight
</P>
<P>
   16. Chicago
</P>
<P>
   Need: A player
</P>
<P>
   Name: Georgia Tech shooting guard Dion Glover (6-5) has been out
since October with a knee injury, but possesses the dreaded monster
talent
</P>
<P>
   17. Atlanta
</P>
<P>
   Needs: Medical insurance, small forward, backups for point guard
and center
</P>
<P>
