<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-29 21:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3897 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LEAH-PERSONALS-SFCHRO     06-29 0753
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LEAH-PERSONALS-SFCHRON </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A QUEEN'S MEAL IS REMEMBERED
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Eds: This story also moved in the ``a'' national news file)  
 By LEAH GARCHIK  
 c.1999 San Francisco Chronicle
