<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-29 21:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3925 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DOWD-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      06-29 0746
