QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-HONDURAN-IMMIG-NYT, which will
move in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``His problem is that he does not want to accept that his father
died. He may have thought that _ I don't know what he thought.''
</P>
<P>
   _JEMMY RODRIGUEZ, a cousin of the boy who said he traveled alone
from Honduras to meet his father at LaGuardia Airport.
</P>
</TEXT>
