<BODY>
 PM-BUDGET-NYT 
 (sw) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; For WEDNESDAY PMs &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Here are the top news stories from The New York Times News
Service for PMs of Wednesday, June 30.
