<P>
   COUNSEL-LAW _ Corruption investigations against high government
officials will change significantly on Wednesday at midnight with
the expiration of the Ethics in Government Act, the law that gave
the country Whitewater prosecutor Kenneth Starr and 19 other
independent counsels in the last two decades. By David Johnston.
</P>
